quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,15,"Ni aŵisile petaka yakunyichisya (matumbi gausito) kuti litakwika mulin’gwedanyichile ŵanganyammwe (litakalyo), ni (aŵisile) sulo kwisa soni matala kuti jenumanja n’dijongolele (mwachimisyene kwakuja)"
  16,16,"Ni (aŵisile soni) imanyisyo (ine yakwajongolela muusi), sano ni ndondwa ŵanganyao akasalijongolela (achimisyene chilo)"
  16,17,Ana Ajula jwaakasagumbaga (jwali Allah) mpaka alandane ni aŵala ŵangaakasagumba (yaili isanamu)? Ana ngankukumbuchila
  16,18,"Soni ntite m’buŵalanje ukoto wa Allah nganim’ba uwwukwanisye. Chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  16,19,Soni Allah akuimanyilila yankuisisa ni yankuilosya papaswela
  16,20,"Sano ayila yaakuilumbanjila yangaŵaga Allah nganiyiŵa igumbile chilichose, nambo yalakweyo ni yaili yagumbidwa"
  16,21,"Ŵawe nganaŵa ŵachijumi, soni ngaakumanyilila kuti tachiukulidwa chakachi (m’malembe)"
  16,22,Nnungu jwenu (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ni Nnungu jumpepe (Allah). Nambo aŵala ŵangaakukulupilila ya Akhera mitima jao jikana (ya Uujika wa Allah) soni ŵanganyao akuŵa ali nkulikwesya
  16,23,Pangali kaichila yanti Allah akuimanyilila yaakuisisa ni yaakuilosya papaswela. Chisimu Jwalakwe jwangaanonyela ŵakulikwesya
  16,24,"Soni naga kuli kuŵechetedwe kukwao yanti: “Ana M’mbuje gwenu jutulwisye chichi (kwa Muhammadi ﷺ)?” Ŵanganyao akasatiji: “Adisiadisi sya ŵandu ŵakala.” (Akuŵechetaga yalakweyi mwakwasokonesya ŵandu)"
  16,25,"Kuti akatwichile misigo jao (jasambi) jakwanila lisiku lya Kiyama, kwisa soni misigo (jasambi) ja aŵala ŵaakwasokonesya mwangali umanyilisi (wa akusokonesedwao). Naalole, kaje kusakala misigo jachakatwichilejejo"
  16,26,"Chisimu ŵaatesile malindi aŵala ŵaŵaliji paujo pao (ŵanya Anamuruda), nambo Allah ŵagumulile chakutaŵa chao kutandila pachitepo, basi nsakasa ni wagwilile pachanya pao, soni ilagasyo ni yaichilile kuumila upande wanganaumanyilila"